\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 It's your general impression that you were pretty well kept working through the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Yes. Yes, I was, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 She bought your time from about seven 'til about nine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Yes. Yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 The men didn't have any supper, late supper or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 
No, they had the evening meal, I don't think they had any drinks or anything after, I don't remember much more. Though of course there's - a lot of grass under the - or water under the bridge since then. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Did you have to do anything like mending there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 
I don't think I did there. No, I don't think I did there, I think it was with the teachers that they realized I was good at darning. I used to get their jobs. But I don't think I did here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 She didn't expect you to do sheets or anything like that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 
No. No. No, she had a sewing machine, she used to do - turn to middle and all that sort of thing conjuring about herself you know. Yes, you're telling me, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 You said you thought you helped out a bit with the ironing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Yes. Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 So quite heavy ironing really?
