ironing was - well it was bad but not all that bad. Don't want to make it worse than it was. It was bad enough. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Was that the job where she fussed about how you did your hair?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 What was it she said you had to do to your hair?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 
I had - I used to put it in a plait down me back, 'cos I was always very proud of it, when I went out - Sunday afternoons I used to get out about three, and be back again by ten, and when I went out I used to plait me hair as I was going to be at home, an
d
 she objected to me leaving the house like it, she said it didn't matter - what I done when I was home, but she didn't like me leaving her house with me hair down me back. 'Cos that was - distinction again wasn't it, I was young. To do that - kind of work
 you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Did you have to wear a cap and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 So your hair would be up -under the cap?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Did she ever fuss about the kind of way your uniform looked and whether it was clean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Can't remember but I expect I done that as much myself as - as far as I could yes. Yes, I should think I done that myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 You don't remember her criticising you in that way?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Just that hairstyle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Did you have to clean their boots at all or shoes, the men?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 
No. I had to buy my - what - what was the row over boot polish? I think I had to buy my own boot polish, and she had a son that was in the Navy, he didn't come home very often, and this time he used mine and I did ruck
. I did have a go. But - I think it blew over, I think I lost it. I can't remember much about that now, I didn't mind him though, he was more - he used to fight his mother and that pleased me. Oh they had one or two big rows.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 What sort of things did they row about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 
One in particular - he used - ordinary jug or mug or something with shaving water. Soapy water in that - so he said, what's the matter with you, he said, you wash them in soapy water? So she said, yes, but they're dried after. You kno}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12072762\charrsid13588098 w, there was that sort of niggle}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098  all the time, she didn't like him anyway.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 He obviously got on her nerves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Mm. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 So you'd have those few hours off on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Did you go to church when you were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 You gave up church going?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Do you think if you'd wanted to go you could have gone in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Would have been difficult, but I suppose I could have - if I'd been in the mood to fight her I would have done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 It didn't come up?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Did she go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 No. No, the son was the sidesman, he used to come in Sunday dinnertime but - she was always there, she didn't go to church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 What about Saturdays, did you have any time off on Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 No, Saturday if anyt
hing was worse than the other days because everything had to be cleaned up and extra beds and everything got ready for Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Because of you being out in the evening you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Did they have a midday hot dinner on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Yes. Yes. That made it late for me to get away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 I'm surprised you got through by three.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Well - well I'm saying three, I - you know, near enough. Could have been later, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 They'd eat about one o'clock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 But you never ate with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 No. No, never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 There was always that difference?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Mm hm. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Were you allowed a fire in your bedroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Oh no, no fires in bedrooms for anybody. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 The bedrooms were unheated?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Yes. Like going up into ice worlds. In fact the water did freeze in their - jugs and basins in their rooms, in all our rooms.
\par 
