 you. No, not in that house anyway because it was all work. Yes, and the - men, as soon as they were - out, they'd be out, one or two of them were courting and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12072762\charrsid13588098 etcetera}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
