\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 She obviously wasn't too keen on you reading a newspaper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14383286 CC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Oh dear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16391728 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4403921\charrsid13588098 Did any of the people you worked for lend you books?
